{"id": 2958, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常里，你是哪种类型的“情怀税”上缴员？", "description": "一看到绝版纸书就走不动道的就是我了。", "record_count": 7512, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190520164815Nhka3vjsWEyIdFgf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-23T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5840, "title": "日常里，你是哪种类型的“情怀税”上缴员？", "content": "日常里，你是哪种类型的“情怀税”上缴员？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 344505, "content": "童年滤镜型，老版总是最经典，翻拍基本扑街", "image": "img/option/option/20190520165820unGJsBy7HA95R8lp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344506, "content": "物以稀为贵型，冠名“绝版/限量版”的总会更想入手", "image": "img/option/option/20190520165920ctr8z14SkfqGRWAN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344508, "content": "人工天然型，手工制品总觉得比机器量产更有味道", "image": "img/option/option/20190520170755pW1FkXtfL4a5EgDZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344509, "content": "old school 型，对复古、有年代感的东西总是欲罢不能", "image": "img/option/option/20190520171630XQR8n9WkMfKulqBr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344512, "content": "理想主义型，对那些坚持认真态度的总会支持一下", "image": "img/option/option/20190520172218pDYV98l0hZcLUwer.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344521, "content": "品牌忠诚型，索尼/苹果/迪奥...大法好", "image": "img/option/option/20190520173630UnzBmyxiZHqcrNCb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344524, "content": "次元信仰型，收集喜欢角色的手办/周边就是我的情怀", "image": "img/option/option/20190520172902V4vm1UnybG3hIx7j.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344528, "content": "传统守护型，仪式性习俗会希望坚持执行", "image": "img/option/option/201905201735211qyFGbXOWMxD0sKf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}